700,"uid":87363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:51:24.000Z","msg":"仲問幾時有新貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食屎啦<br />\n佢以為毛公仔咩<br />\n公主病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1abb244d05335b2459db2f94c77d4d392547b63","tid":2510700,"uid":113007,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:53:41.000Z","msg":"證明家訪都哂鳩氣 無撚意思<br />\n濕鳩義工都有份間接累到隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有心嘅人 點都會對隻貓好<br />\n冇心照顧嘅 更有錢都冇撚用啦<br />\n<br />\n人哋話想退又話諗吓？真奇怪<br />\n（定係濕鳩義工聽到人哋話想退<br />\n教人某啲養貓嘢 所以人哋先再講諗吓先？）<br />\n點解唔即刻接返走隻貓呢！！！<br />\n條仆街已經講想退又話唔退<br />\n聽到都覺得呢啲人癡鳩線啦<br />\n<br />\n其實聽到對方話想退貓<br />\n都已經代表無心繼續去養啦<br />\n佢講得出呢句已經係一個超級危險嘅警告信號<br />\n點解啲貓義工做野可以咁撚求其？！<br />\n<br />\n啲家訪填表申請有乜柒意思？？<br />\n出咗事上嚟連登公審？？<br />\n其實大把棄貓嘅人<br />\n呢啲教訓 聽都唔係唔係第一次啦<br />\n重點係隻貓已經受咗傷害啦"},{"pid":"ac459e66e8019a677632c36629682c598ce836aa","tid":2510700,"uid":333570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a296439d12386fb317738c4cdc92df79d8a8465","tid":2510700,"uid":179723,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ub7mywk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fub7mywk.jpg&h=bd33bef2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日返咗貓星了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝條仆街同虐待動物嘅人不得好死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:53:55.000Z","msg":"貓貓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed75cdc3ebe0bb04fc75cd4c51edf0c208827989","tid":2510700,"uid":113007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a296439d12386fb317